          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fiscal Year 2022 Veterans Affairs Major Medical Facility Authorization Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Veterans Affairs to carry out specified major medical facility projects during FY2022. The bill also indicates the maximum amount that can be spent on each project.</p>]]>
